36:59.592 --> 37:00.676
Don't worry about it.

37:02.595 --> 37:03.763
[Mel] Where's the food?

37:06.224 --> 37:07.725
[groans quietly] Sorry, I…

37:09.644 --> 37:10.853
forgot that was the plan.

37:11.520 --> 37:14.273
It's fine. I can figure something out.

37:17.068 --> 37:18.110
[bottle clinks]

37:21.405 --> 37:22.406
[Mel] Are you okay?

37:23.783 --> 37:26.077
Yeah, just a long day.

37:26.869 --> 37:30.498
[Mel] Well, I was gonna surprise you,
but I have no patience.

37:30.581 --> 37:31.582
[chuckles] So,

37:33.125 --> 37:34.961
I got us tickets to Maui.

37:35.544 --> 37:37.755
