39:12.516 --> 39:13.476
[Jack] I'm sorry.

39:19.357 --> 39:20.316
You know what?

39:22.485 --> 39:23.486
It's okay.

39:25.321 --> 39:27.239
We can wait until you're ready.

39:27.823 --> 39:28.699
Okay?

39:29.700 --> 39:31.827
[emotional music playing]

39:31.911 --> 39:36.832
